<paragraph id="D72736F3E110FF94FF6D14F6FEB9FD5E" blockId="72.[151,1437,476,2015]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">
<emphasis id="E5ECEAE1E110FF94FF6D14F6FE9FFE5A" bold="true" box="[151,276,476,503]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">Diagnosis:</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="10984D70E110FF94FEE114F7FE76FE5A" authority="Ferrari, 2019" authorityName="Ferrari" authorityYear="2019" box="[283,509,477,503]" class="Insecta" family="Colletidae" genus="Colletes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sertanicola" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis id="E5ECEAE1E110FF94FEE114F7FE76FE5A" box="[283,509,477,503]" italics="true" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">Colletes sertanicola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="E5ECEAE1E110FF94FDFE14F7FDC8FE5A" bold="true" box="[516,579,477,503]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="FEDF579AE110FF94FDFE14F7FDC8FE5A" box="[516,579,477,503]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
can be readily diagnosed by the combination of F1 relatively long, 1.3/1.1x (
<specimenCount id="C19EFD7AE110FF94FF58172AFF3FFDB6" box="[162,180,512,539]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" type="female">♀</specimenCount>
/♁) as long as its apical width, and T1–T2 pale-brown (except T1–T2 dark-brown anteriorly in the male). The male of 
<taxonomicName id="10984D70E110FF94FF0F170FFE5CFD92" authority="Ferrari, 2019" authorityName="Ferrari" authorityYear="2019" box="[245,471,549,575]" class="Insecta" family="Colletidae" genus="Colletes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="sertanicola" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis id="E5ECEAE1E110FF94FF0F170FFE5CFD92" box="[245,471,549,575]" italics="true" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">Colletes sertanicola</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="E5ECEAE1E110FF94FE25170FFD94FD92" bold="true" box="[479,543,549,575]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="FEDF579AE110FF94FE25170FFD94FD92" box="[479,543,549,575]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
is most similar to that of 
<taxonomicName id="10984D70E110FF94FCBC170FFC27FD92" authority="Ferrari, 2019" authorityName="Ferrari" authorityYear="2019" box="[838,940,549,575]" class="Insecta" family="Colletidae" genus="Colletes" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chicoi" status="n. sp.">
<emphasis id="E5ECEAE1E110FF94FCBC170FFC27FD92" box="[838,940,549,575]" italics="true" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">C. chicoi</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<emphasis id="E5ECEAE1E110FF94FC4E170FFC7FFD92" bold="true" box="[948,1012,549,575]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73">
<taxonomicNameLabel id="FEDF579AE110FF94FC4E170FFC7FFD92" box="[948,1012,549,575]" pageId="72" pageNumber="73" rank="species">n. sp.</taxonomicNameLabel>
</emphasis>
