<paragraph id="D72736F3E111FF95FF3D1257FBDEF816" blockId="73.[151,1437,153,1979]" pageId="73" pageNumber="74">Part of the holotype’s head (specially the genal and occipital areas) as well as its pronotum and anterior mesoscutal area are covered with white glue. Otherwise the specimen is in good condition.</paragraph>
